The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Hosts to face Pak in opener 
Islamabad: Pakistan alongwith New Zealand will take part in a tri-series in Sri Lanka from May 10. Pakistan will play Sri Lanka in the opening match in Dambulla. The schedule May 10: Sri Lanka vs Pakistan; May 11: Pakistan vs New Zealand; May 13: Sri Lanka vs New Zealand (all three matches at Dambulla); May 17: Sri Lanka vs Pakistan; May 18: Sri Lanka vs New Zealand; May 19: Pakistan vs New Zealand (all three matches at SSC ground in Colombo); May 23: Final (d/n) in Colombo. (PTI)  Copyright 
